        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……不能戴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸，着打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷叫你戴你就戴上得了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞给甲戴手铐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，您瞧这走到街上多不是样儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这还有个名堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫做："
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解差常把犯人害，自作自受倒发解。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱行者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解差甲、解差乙、焦赞同下。）"
        }
      ],
