    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘利华",
        "刘妻",
        "焦赞",
        "解差乙",
        "解差甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘利华 （扑灯蛾） 夫妻双双开店房，开店房，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "接待旅客日夜忙；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赃官恶棍命必亡，命必亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，刘利华。自幼爱习拳棒，在这三岔路口开了一座小小的店房。看今日天气"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晴和，不免将老婆唤出，把幌儿挂起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆，老婆，老婆走出来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻开草店，惯打抱不平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么事啊？大郎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日天气晴和，将幌儿挂起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就依大郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘利华 （耍孩儿） 三岔口开店房，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "接旅客日夜忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华下。焦赞、二解差同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，天不早了，咱们该打店了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去打店。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，您倒是把这个给我摘下来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，这是朝廷的王法，不能摘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有得，这句话在这儿等着我哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷，伺候您一道儿，给他摘下来得啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看在你的份上，我也给你个“瞒上不瞒下”，与他摘下来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前去打店。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妈呀！这哪是我解着他，简直是他解着我啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解差甲见刘妻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "借问一声，哪儿有店呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你出门就没带着眼睛吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八成儿有一对。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没看见？这不是店吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店主婆请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有上房？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有，随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一同进店！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞、解差甲、解差乙同进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明灯两盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要两盏灯干什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两处安歇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿，那可不行！别的由着你，的地方可有不了你！一处安歇，一处安歇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼！两处安歇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎伙计，什么一处两处的，两处就两处吧。你怎么这么死心眼儿呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得，得，两处，两处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻取两盏灯。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此客官请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻引路，开门，焦赞持灯进入，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说伙计，这个起我简直受不了啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依我看……"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依你便怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依我啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解差乙向解差甲耳语。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对对对！咱们先睡觉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店婆子，店婆子！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻在外偷听，闻声进入。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这儿哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说，你怎么净顾着那个黑大个儿，不管我们了？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻有意识地说。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个黑大个儿好横啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焦二虎嘛，不横！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，焦二虎……"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，怎么啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪不得他那么横哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼，他横，我看他横到几时？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解差乙暗止之。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店婆子，我们在哪儿睡呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻引路，开门，解差甲、解差乙同进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，小心火烛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解差甲、解差乙轻薄地说。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解差甲、解差乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用你老操心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解差甲、解差乙同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！闻听人言：三关上将焦赞杀死奸党，充军发配。适才听解差言道："
        }
      ],
