    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "任堂惠",
        "刘利华",
        "刘妻",
        "焦赞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！他在前面走，俺在后面赶，赶到此处，为何不见焦二哥？来此已是三岔"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "口。且住！此处有一店房，想是他们住在此店，待俺问个明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，呔店家！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住店的吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。我且问你，有两个解差，解押一个黑脸大汉，可住在此处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个黑……嗯，没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有清净的房屋？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有，您请吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带路！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华、任堂惠同进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，店家，店家！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来啦。用些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明灯一盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "灯到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿过去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天时不早，各讨方便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请便！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走着哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "擦擦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华擦桌子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你与我走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华出门，旋转回。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转来做甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忘了嘱咐你一句话，要小心点……"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小心什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小心这灯头火！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！看那店家鬼鬼祟祟，甚是可疑，二哥的去向他比知晓。也罢，俺今晚就"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在此处查看动静便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠巡视，睡下。刘利华上，欲拨门，刘妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这小子扎手，我来帮你吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用，你去料理那两个解差，我对付这个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对，你我分头动起手来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻下。刘利华拨门，进门，摸索，任堂惠惊觉，搏斗，正在难解难分时，焦赞、刘妻同上，黑暗中任堂"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惠与焦赞、刘利华与刘妻互相扭打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠、刘利华",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（什么人）（谁）？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞、刘妻",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞。什么人？）（当家的，是我。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任堂惠在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘利华急取灯。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟因何到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暗地保护二哥来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，闹了半天，白打了一宿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下刘利华，这是我的老婆。方才不知，以为您是来害焦二爷的哪！哎呀，冒"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "犯！冒犯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。你夫妻如此仗义，真乃难得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠看众人。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，刘仁兄，解差何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早叫我给杀了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀的好！杀死解差，你夫妻在此多有不便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何不同到三关？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘利华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位言之有理，后店一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焦赞请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
